cs.FL, cs.DS, cs.LO, cs.IT, cs.CC 

Reasoning: 
- cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory) is the most likely category as the paper deals with regular languages and automata. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is also likely as the paper discusses the state complexity of languages. 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is relevant as the paper deals with syntactic complexity, which is related to logical complexity. 
- cs.IT (Information Theory) is relevant as the paper discusses bounds on the complexity of languages. 
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with complexity measures of regular languages.
